Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these sub-disciplines also deal with topics related to wireless networks, spatial modeling, and performance analysis.
